<table style="-qt-table-type: root; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:5px; margin-right:5px;">
<tr>
<td style="border: none;">
<p><span>Time got the better of us whilst we were away, and I don't think we were ever up to date with our blogs! We did mean to catch up in the 7 weeks that we were home, but that didn't happen either. Now we are away again, so it looks like the final two weeks of Ghana will have to be put on hold even longer until we're back and have time to look through our journals and write something actually worth reading.</span>
</p>
<p><span>In the meantime we are going to do our best to keep up to date for this trip! Otherwise a year's worth of blogs to write when we get back will take forever/never happen!!</span>
</p>
<p><span>Love Jo and Tom xx</span>
</p></td>
</tr>
