   <decoration/>
   <text applySpotColor="0" areaTextType="content">
    <![CDATA[
<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd">

<html>
<head>
<meta content="1" name="qrichtext"/>
<style type="text/css">p { margin-bottom:50px; }</style>
</head>
<body style="font-family:'Calibri'; font-size:16pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
<table style="-qt-table-type: root; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:5px; margin-right:5px;">
<tr>
<td style="border: none;">
<p><span>Ho ho ho Hoi An! Christmas this year was spent in the joyus town that is Hoi An (Incase you didn't get the joke!)</span>
</p>
<p><span>Our very nice and WARM christmas was spent lounging by the riverside (in our santa hats), cruising down the river (in our santa hats) and taking part in a gourmet cooking course at the Red Bridge cooking school in their outdoor kitchen terrace.... (in our santa hats!)</span>
</p>
<p><span>Rather than bore you with the details, here are lots of photos of us on our Vietnamese Christmas Day :D &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p><span>That's all folks, hope you like the photos and a very Merry Christmas to you all!</span>
</p>
<p><span>Lotsa love, Tom &amp;amp; Jo</span>
</p>
<p><span>xxxx</span>
</p></td>
</tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
